author: @chinmayeejoshi4592
text: Couldn't agree more! TBH, non-tech companies are set to benefit most from the stable use cases, as they seek to enhance their bottomlines amidst current market conditions. In my own experience, I've observed there is SO much context that employees hold in their heads - there needs to be a reliable way to capture all that and that way is a combination of neural search and text classification.. "Alexa, Dan at WholeFoods won't take this delivery next week because he's on vacation. Tell the next delivery driver to ask for Sherry instead!" These are the efficiencies they seek!
